Resource Profile: CH LAB Observation Results: eGFR - MDRD Profile for males

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-lab-report/StructureDefinition/ch-lab-observation-egfr-mdrd-male Version: 1.0.0-ballot
Active as of 2024-05-17 Computable Name: ChLabObservation_eGFR_MDRD_male

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

Renal function can be determined by laboratory measurement of serum creatinine, from which the estimated glomerular (eGFR_MDMR) filtration rate can be calculated.

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Observation/Observation-eGFR-MDRD-male
